data.description: Welcome to 363 Hollow Cove Road in the highly sought after Westcott Ridge subdivision! Discover the epitome of luxurious living in this 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath home, where comfort meets sophistication. Boasting an office with a closet, this residence offers the perfect blend of functional space and modern design. Step inside to an open floor plan adorned with coffered ceilings, creating an inviting atmosphere that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The kitchen, features a gas stove, perfect for culinary enthusiasts, and an inviting eat-in area for casual dining. Escape to the loft area, ideal for relaxation or entertainment, and relish the convenience of a Bluetooth-connected home, ensuring seamless connectivity throughout. The oversized master bedroom provides a tranquil retreat, while the home's design is complemented by an amazing oversized laundry room, adding both convenience and charm. The four seasons room beckons, inviting you to enjoy the outdoors year-round, overlooking the fenced-in yard - a perfect haven for pets or private gatherings. Warm up by the gas fireplace or entertain guests on the patio. Beyond the walls of this exquisite residence, embrace the award-winning Lexington/Richland District 5 schools and neighborhood amenities including a pool, clubhouse, and playground. Strategically located close to I-26, commuting becomes a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to call 363 Hollow Cove Road home—schedule your showing today!
